high_descs: look down and walk straight towards the window and turn left and walk straight to the counter and turn left
pick up the tomato in front of the knife on the table
turn right and walk straight towards the counter and then turn left and walk straight to the microwave
open the microwave and put the tomato inside and close it, set the timer and then open the microwave and remove the tomato and close the door
turn around and walk straight towards the fridge and then turn right and walk straight towards the edge of the counter and turn left and look down
put the tomato into the trash can on the floor
anns.task_desc: cook a tomato then throw it away in the trash can

high_descs: Walk towards the wall then hang a left and walk over to the kitchen island.
Pick up the leftmost tomato off of the island.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave then microwave the tomato for a couple seconds, after that take it out and close the microwave.
Walk over to the white bin to the right of the fridge.
Put the heated tomato in the white bin to the right of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in a white bin.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn left before reaching the garbage can on the floor, then walk to the kitchen island in the center of the room.
Pick up the tomato in front of the large knife.
Turn right, walk forward to the counter, then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Heat the tomato for a few seconds in the microwave, then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn around, walk forward to the wall, then turn right and walk forward past the refrigerator, then turn left towards the garbage can on the floor.
Put the tomato in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot tomato in a garbage can.
